OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely cloudy day, with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain. Rain may turn heavy
OL,7,Fand showery through the middle of the
OL,8,Fday and into the afternoon. Light
OL,9,Fwinds. Mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FRemaining largely cloudy
OL,12,Fthrough the evening and much of the
OL,13,Fnight, as rain slowly clears eastward.
OL,14,FBecoming dry and chilly from the west
OL,15,Flate in the night. Light winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FCloudy to start, gradually
OL,18,Fturning brighter from the west as any
OL,19,Flingering rain clears eastern coasts.
OL,20,FA band of showers will likely move
OL,21,Feastward later in the day. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
